OL,3,CBus company launches campaign against
OL,4,Canti-social and abusive behaviour
OL,6,FA bus company has launched a campaign
OL,7,Fto remind passengers that bus drivers
OL,8,Fand staff are real human beings with
OL,9,Ffelings, as they try to tackle anti-
OL,10,Fsocial behaviour on board.
OL,12,FWith the campaign, Borders Buses wants
OL,13,Fto encourage more respect for their
OL,14,Fstaff, and has partnered with Police
OL,15,FScotland and Scottish Borders Council
OL,16,Fto get the message across.
