OL,3,CBus company launches campaign against
OL,4,Canti-social and abusive behaviour
OL,6,FMike Carmoodie told ITV Border: "Over
OL,7,Fthe last six months I think it's
OL,8,Fescalated quite a lot... I've seen a
OL,9,Flot, heard a lot. Kids getting more
OL,10,Fvocal, older people as well - it's not
OL,11,Fjust the young ones.
OL,13,F"It's amazing how the drivers put up
OL,14,Fwith it. If you try to intervene
OL,15,Fyou'll get a lot of abuse - verbal, or
OL,16,Fthey'll start throwing apples or eggs
OL,17,Fand things."
