OL,6,FAnother driver said that passengers
OL,7,Fwho intervene with anti-social
OL,8,Fbehaviour sometimes become the target
OL,9,Fof abuse themselves.
OL,11,FMichael Ramsay said: "I've seen quite
OL,12,Fa few (incidents) over the years I've
OL,13,Fbeen here... it's a lot of kids
OL,14,Fpicking on other kids, being quite
OL,15,Fabusive, especially to other people
OL,16,Fwhen they're trying to help them.
