OL,6,F"It just gets out of hand, and
OL,7,Fobviously there's no power to do
OL,8,Fanything, which is quite hard as well.
OL,9,FBecause you're the port of call,
OL,10,Fyou're going to bear the brunt of
OL,11,Fwhatever they're feeling at the time."
OL,13,FA Borders Buses communications
OL,14,Fdirector said that she expected the
OL,15,Fproblem to worsen over the Christmas
OL,16,Fperiod, suggesting that with Christmas
OL,17,Fparties, people might "use the bus for
OL,18,Fthe first time in a year".
