OL,3,CBus company launches campaign against
OL,4,Canti-social and abusive behaviour
OL,6,FSharon Morrison said: "As well as the
OL,7,Fhappiness that goes along with people
OL,8,Fbeing merry, there is the other side
OL,9,Fwhere people can be aggressive."
OL,11,FMs Morrison also pointed out, however,
OL,12,Fthat drunkenness is not the only cause
OL,13,Fof abusiveness, nor is it a problem
OL,14,Fcaused only by young people.
