OL,6,FShe said anti-social behaviour also
OL,7,Fcame from "customers that are running
OL,8,Flate for work or appointments," adding
OL,9,Fthat "this isn't necessarily people
OL,10,Fout drinking, this is a general
OL,11,Ffeeling, and we do want to point out
OL,12,Fthat it's not just old people."
